    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="structDali_1_1FreeList" kindref="compound">FreeList</ref> operates by connecting unused elements of a vector together in a linked list using the value of each unused cell as a pointer to the next. When a new element is added, it will be added to the first free index of the vector and the new free index will be the value which was on that cell. </para>
    </briefdescription>
